-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party dependencies
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

libsodium
  URL:     https://github.com/jedisct1/libsodium
  License: ISC License
  Usage:   XChaCha20-Poly1305 AEAD encryption, Argon2id key derivation,
           secure memory operations (sodium_malloc, sodium_memzero, mlock).
  Note:    Linked as a system library; not bundled in this repository.

OpenSSL (libcrypto)
  URL:     https://github.com/openssl/openssl
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Usage:   AES-256-GCM AEAD encryption, HKDF-SHA-256 key derivation.
  Note:    Linked as a system library; not bundled in this repository.

BLAKE3
  URL:     https://github.com/BLAKE3-team/BLAKE3
  License: CC0-1.0 OR Apache-2.0 WITH LLVM-exception
  Usage:   Per-shard public-header binding hash included as AEAD associated
           data for every chunk in that shard.
  Note:    Bundled as a git submodule under submodules/blake3 and built
           automatically by CMake. Source files carry their own license headers.

Argon2 (phc-winner-argon2)
  URL:     https://github.com/P-H-C/phc-winner-argon2
  License: CC0-1.0 OR Apache-2.0
  Usage:   Passphrase hardening via Argon2id; invoked through the KDF layer.
  Note:    Bundled as a git submodule under submodules/argon2 and built
           automatically by CMake. Source files carry their own license headers.
